{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"readonly"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"coordinate"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation\/coordinate"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Property","externalID":"c:objc(pl)MLNAnnotation(py)coordinate","symbolKind":"property","title":"coordinate","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"coordinate"}],"fragments":[{"text":"coordinate","kind":"identifier"}]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The center point (specified as a map coordinate) of the annotation. (required)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(read-only)"}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation\/coordinate"]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation/coordinate":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation\/coordinate","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"coordinate"}],"title":"coordinate","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The center point (specified as a map coordinate) of the annotation. (required)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(read-only)"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation\/coordinate","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","role":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}]}}}